@node "FUTURE" "Planned Enhancements"
@next "PROGRAMMTEILE"
@prev "VERSIONEN"

  First of all I must admit that I cannot guarantee any further development
  of this program. This also depends heavily on new registrations.

  @{u}The following changes and extensions are planned:@{uu}

  - Interfaces to other music sources.

@{b}  - An automatic installation script.@{ub}
    
  - In any case I will try to release a PowerUp version!
  
  - Some modifications to the hyperhelp calls and other requesters.

